Please do take the time to check out their project, there are investment levels for all, so maybe put some of that ETH to good use rather than deleting it on another rug. With all that's going on atm let's push these good news projects to the front.

This is going to be BIG.

The artwork is insane, website smooth AF and the whole team has put together something incredible. They already have some major partners like @Zeneca_33  and will soon be coming onto the @RCSPod to discuss it in depth.

Their project mantra is to secure at-risk land in the Amazon rainforest to stop deforestation and protect its biodiversity. As a holder or "guardian" you are fostering sustainable activity that benefits the land and the people who live there.
Everyone should be taking a look at their project! @nemus_earth  is the epitomy of a collectible NFT with real world utility for good, that goes way above a small % of mint going to a charity.

We all hit it off instantly and ended up spending most of #ETHDenver hanging out. From Big Dad Energy at the CryptoDads IRL event, chatting DAOs at 3am in the castle (with some scotch) and VIP at Major Lazer in the Temple... we already have plans to hang out again.

Being the nice guys that we are, me & @CalcioNFT  decided to wait with @reachn4thetop in the 3 hour COVID test line despite having ours already and im glad that we did as we were fortunate enough to meet @Biaaancaaa  & @muninn23  from @nemus_earth.

It's a weird thing to say but a few of the main highlights for me from #ETHDenver came when standing in line or queueing (as us brits say).
